\backslash 
sim l^2$. Up to $l~
\backslash 
sim10$~AU, the density is smaller and the poloidal speed is larger for the wind with a larger $
\backslash 
beta$ value. }
\end_inset 


\layout Standard


\begin_inset LatexCommand \label{fig:discwind_vr_rho}

\end_inset 


\layout Standard


\begin_inset ERT
status Open

\layout Standard

\backslash 
end{figure*}
\end_inset 


\layout Standard


\begin_inset ERT
status Open

\layout Standard
