caption{Comparison of of the wind model with and without the optically-thick and geometrically-thin disc.  The latter can be also equivalent to a model with a large inner radius of the accretion disc in which none of the wind emission region is not blocked provided the inclination is moderate. The left panel shows the profile computed with $i=55^{
\backslash 
